{"tid":1452843,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急！愈嬲愈要睇！嚟緊點做全民運動！","createTime":"2019-08-12T02:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:43:27.000Z","uid":270394,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5868b6bd20a7b7a848e6ae0994535edf7872eaed","tid":1452843,"uid":270394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:32:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">相信無人不憤怒，因為沒憤怒的都不是人。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n但除憤怒以外，我們應當如何？<br />\n<br />\n謹記梁天琦在獄中的預警，不要被憤怒蒙蔽我們，而失去計劃思考。<br />\n以眼還眼，此仇必報。但應如何去報？<br />\n行動必須以針對警察、警權為先!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我而家要嘅，唔止係人，係每個人手上嘅iPad!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n短期全民行動：<br />\n1.收集警暴事件片段，輯錄短片製作文宣！<br />\n2.全民於所有公眾地方，手持iPad向外播放，地鐵、巴士、街頭、餐廳；<br />\n3.買手提投影機，於警署外、大空館、機場、禮賓府、尖沙咀等投映；（具意義的地方一齊再諗）<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n重點係要不停放大721、811，以全民運動減少衝突場面，如此放任殺入警暴下，更多義士唔止送頭<br />\n，隨時有更多爆頭！</span></span>"},{"pid":"6862ede0c6c558a6a27548f596a4b464a3954296","tid":1452843,"uid":270394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:32:31.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"64f128cb706f9601ad5161ebbed61f527521594a","tid":1452843,"uid":270394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:32:44.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"32a7ab27c6faed0d41a7befc2e8f4fd2e44a6342","tid":1452843,"uid":270394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:34:35.000Z","msg":"推到文宣組見到！"},{"pid":"d7b6154b669b45556b683737a89177f2455245e3","tid":1452843,"uid":161125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:34:38.000Z","msg":"文宣要多做!! 唔可以俾佢地白白送頭!"},{"pid":"ad403645df0cbedfb8a38720017c932b982365e3","tid":1452843,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:35:09.000Z","msg":"重新整理<br />\n記者可唔可以有共識！！<br />\n呢啲係我哋最關心嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n<strong>每日無論邊個問先，頭幾條都要係呢幾條！！<br />\n每一次問都數， 呢條問題係第幾次第幾日問，未有答案！ 幾時先會有答案？</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">請準備好每條問題嘅影片及圖片</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 721點解唔執法？點解只告非法集會？點解全部未落charge？<br />\n播圖播片<br />\n指揮官喺村公所同白衣人對話，當時佢哋手持武器， 點解唔執法？<br />\n播片<br />\n<br />\n2 有證據顯示警方用過期Tear Gas?用咗幾多?點解用?<br />\n請準備圖及片<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n過期催淚彈 成分變質變山埃， 警方會否道歉及賠償？<br />\n<br />\n3. 警察係咪扮示威者，然後執法？ 點解用咁嘅策略 ？點證明佢哋冇掉磚？冇煽動？冇放火？會否Charge佢哋參與暴動?<br />\n準備圖及片<br />\n<br />\n4. 點解會係地鐵站 內放催淚彈同胡椒彈？目的係驅趕定拘捕？<br />\n準備片<br />\nFollow up questions<br />\n如果係驅趕，佢哋已經喺地鐵站走緊！ 點解仲要放？ 如果係拘捕，你應該衝入去拉人而唔係放催淚彈胡椒彈！可唔可以解釋下<br />\n<strong>預設答案：</strong>情況混亂，個別事件<br />\nfollow up questions<br />\n警察冇專業訓練處理混亂情況？<br />\n個別例子係合理解釋？殺人放火強姦都係個別例子！ 示威者都係混亂情況下先做出唔尋常，唔理智行為，警方接唔接受呢個解釋唔落charge？<br />\n<br />\n5. 有片影到警察放武器入示威者背囊，點解？係唔係插贓嫁禍？<br />\n<strong>預設答案&nbsp;：</strong>&nbsp;冇資料<br />\n預備嗰條片， 講埋時間地點<br />\n叫佢解釋！<br />\n<br />\n6. 太古零距離開槍， 做法是否恰當？咩原因同情況下要咁做？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n7. 北角警察無視白衣人攻擊黑衣人及記者， 荃灣白衣人 一離場，場警察就進場，又係一個巧合？<br />\n準備片<br />\n<br />\n一齊畀意見！！<br />\n葵芳地鐵站內放催淚彈<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fchishing87%2Fvideos%2F10156292523426674%2F&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=7c268ae5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/chishing87/videos/10156292523426674/</a><br />\n<br />\n追打並推落扶手電梯<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196364073824126&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=418fd552\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196364073824126</a><br />\n<br />\n太古站開槍 1米內射示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424996360930416&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=dc46bc01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424996360930416</a><br />\n<br />\n竹支嫁禍<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F2424974427599276&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=92ac9dd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/2424974427599276</a><br />\n<br />\n唔回應是否扮示威者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkincident%2Fpermalink%2F2196515767142290&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=00154ff3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkincident/permalink/2196515767142290</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記者會共識<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449180</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b671f8b6212fd3af8f6729162bd9e401d08d566d","tid":1452843,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:35:11.000Z","msg":"要番工嘅 呼籲同事停止辦公<br />\n<br />\n罷工的工人群眾可能會聚集在工作場所外面，勸說其他同僚參與罷工，或嘗試阻止僱主與客戶的交易來往。零售或服務行業的罷工稱為「罷市」。另一種罷工方式是工人留守在工作場所內，但拒絕工作或拒絕離開。<br />\n<br />\n也有罷工工人會以只完成工作的最基本要求以示抗議，此方式稱為「怠工」或「按章工作」。例如，工人可能會格外嚴格地執行所有安全守則，從而減低工作效率；<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/罷工\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5&d=hP6DzN64O1sWLJLr9GARkdUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=fed94692\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/罷工</a>"},{"pid":"06e06e1bcfff98ac78fb0138ff68539bdf73bb09","tid":1452843,"uid":270394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:41:56.000Z","msg":"大家罷工又好，返工又好，帶埋部iPad，一齊周圍將警暴全港放映！"},{"pid":"96df87d2bf7599aa2bed89605986f460f3b65020","tid":1452843,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"前線先休養生息，淨係尋晚己經好多材料，文宣組係時候全力出擊"},{"pid":"2f9fc9f36dcebb4bd38d8d449e885243e37858cf","tid":1452843,"uid":270394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96df87d2bf7599aa2bed89605986f460f3b65020","tid":1452843,"uid":137627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:42:10.000Z","msg":"前線先休養生息，淨係尋晚己經好多材料，文宣組係時候全力出擊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T02:43:27.000Z","msg":"要召喚文宣組，全港send片播片"}]}